56
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:32,120
Despite the fact that she and I are in love...

57
00:03:34,250 --> 00:03:37,850
{\an8}I presume!

58
00:03:35,030 --> 00:03:39,430
Captain of the Flying Pirates
Vander Decken IX

59
