Bullhead Shark Fishman

60
00:03:37,850 --> 00:03:40,040
{\an8}Princess Shirahoshi!

61
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:47,640
No matter how long I wander the ocean floor, I'll never find another woman as great or as beautiful as you!

62
00:03:48,010 --> 00:03:50,600
If our love is mutual, then all is well.

63
